g4 = sns.JointGrid(x='qsec', y='wt', data=data,space=0, ratio=2)
i=1
for quarter, sales in data.groupby('carb'):
    sns.kdeplot(sales.qsec, ax=g4.ax_marg_x, label='Q'+str(i));
    sns.kdeplot(sales.wt, ax=g4.ax_marg_y, vertical=True, 
             label='Q'+str(i));
    g4.ax_joint.plot(sales.qsec,sales.wt,"D", ms=5)
    i +=1
    g4.ax_marg_x.set_title('4\. Scatter Plot - Histogram with hue, KDE on m')
